title: Gov't Mule - The Deep End (2002) (3CD) [EAC - FLAC]
description:
After the death of bass guitarist Allen Woody, the band began recording tracks using bass players that Woody had admired. Originally, there was to be one disc, but so many musicians wanted to be part of the sessions that over 160 minutes of music was recorded - so 3 CDs were released Volume 1 & 2 with studio recordings and Hidden Treasures with live recordings.
